divs: sighting detailsi went out on my balcony with my canon powershot digital camera on night mode\shot and noticed a bright white light in the sky (east). it kept changing from white to orange to multicolor orbs and different shapes. it made a v-like formation and changed back. it moved around in a jerking motion. some i jerked the camera to try to keep it centered. i finally lost track of it as it went behind a tree next to my building and then past the building out of my line of sight. i felt like this was definitely not a plane or anything else conventional. i heard no sound, felt no strange effects. i was amazed by what i saw.
Summary: Observed bright white object in sky from 2nd floor balcony
